\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb30 \strokec16 Yixuan gains extra Sheer Force based on her Max HP, with every 1 point of Max HP increasing Sheer Force by 0.1.\cb1 \
\cb30 All 
\f0\b \cf25 \strokec25 Auric\'a0Ink DMG
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  Yixuan deals via her skills is Sheer DMG, ignoring enemy DEF and using her Sheer Force stat as the DMG Multiplier.\cb1 \
\cb30 When Yixuan accumulates 
\f0\b \cf25 \strokec25 Auric\'a0Ink Anomaly Buildup
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , it uses an independent Anomaly Buildup gauge, and when triggering an Anomaly, she restores an additional 10 Adrenaline. This can trigger once every 10s.\cb1 \
\cb30 Upon entering combat, Yixuan immediately restores all Adrenaline. In Investigation Zone Mode, this effect can only trigger once every 180s. Triggering a Perfect Dodge grants an additional 5 Adrenaline and can occur at most once per second.\cb1 \
\cb30 When she consumes Adrenaline, Yixuan accumulates Technique Points, gaining 0.667 points for each point of Adrenaline consumed. With enough Technique Points, she can trigger an additional Ultimate: Endless Talisman Suppression. The maximum for Technique Points is 120.\cb1 \
\cb30 The DMG dealt by Yixuan's Basic Attack: Auric Array, Basic Attack: Qingming Eruption, EX Special Attack, Assist Follow-Up, Chain Attack, and Ultimate increases by 
\f0\b \cf31 \strokec31 60%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
